# Komponen UI

Proyek ini menggunakan serangkaian komponen Vue.js yang dapat digunakan kembali, terletak di direktori [resources/js/Components](mdc:resources/js/Components).

## Komponen Tombol

- [PrimaryButton](mdc:resources/js/Components/PrimaryButton.vue) - Tombol utama untuk aksi positif
- [SecondaryButton](mdc:resources/js/Components/SecondaryButton.vue) - Tombol sekunder untuk aksi tambahan
- [DangerButton](mdc:resources/js/Components/DangerButton.vue) - Tombol untuk aksi berbahaya/hapus

## Komponen Input

- [TextInput](mdc:resources/js/Components/TextInput.vue) - Field input teks standar
- [SelectInput](mdc:resources/js/Components/SelectInput.vue) - Dropdown select
- [Checkbox](mdc:resources/js/Components/Checkbox.vue) - Checkbox input
- [InputLabel](mdc:resources/js/Components/InputLabel.vue) - Label untuk input
- [InputError](mdc:resources/js/Components/InputError.vue) - Pesan error untuk input

## Komponen Navigasi

- [Navbar](mdc:resources/js/Components/Navbar.vue) - Navigasi utama
- [NavLink](mdc:resources/js/Components/NavLink.vue) - Link navigasi
- [Dropdown](mdc:resources/js/Components/Dropdown.vue) - Menu dropdown
- [DropdownLink](mdc:resources/js/Components/DropdownLink.vue) - Link dalam dropdown
- [ResponsiveNavLink](mdc:resources/js/Components/ResponsiveNavLink.vue) - Link navigasi responsif

## Komponen Layout

- [SectionMain](mdc:resources/js/Components/SectionMain.vue) - Container utama
- [SectionTitle](mdc:resources/js/Components/SectionTitle.vue) - Judul section
- [SectionFullScreen](mdc:resources/js/Components/SectionFullScreen.vue) - Tampilan fullscreen
- [Modal](mdc:resources/js/Components/Modal.vue) - Dialog modal
- [ConfirmationModal](mdc:resources/js/Components/ConfirmationModal.vue) - Modal konfirmasi

## Komponen Tabel

- [TableCheckboxCell](mdc:resources/js/Components/TableCheckboxCell.vue) - Cell checkbox untuk tabel
- [TableSampleClients](mdc:resources/js/Components/TableSampleClients.vue) - Contoh tabel klien

## Komponen User

- [UserAvatar](mdc:resources/js/Components/UserAvatar.vue) - Avatar pengguna
- [UserAvatarCurrentUser](mdc:resources/js/Components/UserAvatarCurrentUser.vue) - Avatar pengguna yang login
- [UserCard](mdc:resources/js/Components/UserCard.vue) - Kartu informasi pengguna

